title.narrative: Improved availability and quality of data on health and HIV in UNICEF.

description.narrative: The Health and HIV team kept on track all planned activities and undertaken considerable additional analyses related to COVID19 except some field engagement work.. Key results include the launch of the WHO-UNICEF joint immunization estimates, UNICEF brochure plus a set of regional immunization and country specific immunization profiles; launch of the latest HIV estimates for mothers and children including interactive country dashboards and analyses on COVID19 implications for new infections; launch of malaria country profiles with a COVID19 orientation and launch of a pneumonia brochure and associated country snapshots. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:30/06/2020
